Rating: 3
I substituted dijon mustard for the whipping cream, and added a little lemon juice and some dill to the vinaigrette. I needed only one can of chicken broth and didn't heat the artichoke hearts. These changes made for a more flavorful and firmer textured dish, which was pretty popular. Some people even asked for the recipe. I will definitely make it again!

